{"tid":2173843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺唔覺，改左檢疫方法，即刻確診數字減少","createTime":"2020-08-25T13:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T13:19:49.000Z","uid":73783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bdee0c6c88b279c146fa7eda2a8691b2b731afc6","tid":2173843,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"大家覺唔覺好奇怪<br />\n其實呢2個星期<br />\n咩都冇做過<br />\n大家如常出街，返工<br />\n但人數就由百幾跌到幾十<br />\n<br />\n在呢段時間<br />\n改變既只係內地醫療人員來港<br />\n並由飛沬檢測改做深喉檢測<br />\n確診人數就減少左<br />\n<br />\n有2個可能<br />\n1. 深喉檢測唔準，更多false negative<br />\n2. 更多人害怕深喉檢測或被提取dna 送中，而有病都不去做檢測<br />\n<br />\n但由於中招多是廢老，佢地相信政府，看來2. 不太有可能<br />\n<br />\n所以我懷疑深喉檢測既成效<br />\n事實上，我認為而家比之前係更危險<br />\n有更多false negative周圍走<br />\n佢地自己有事都唔知<br />\n所以大家，保護好自己"},{"pid":"b0f405afa15fac4b304441ea1513ae97e1df6d00","tid":2173843,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"取消左立法會選舉即刻冇哂啲確診"},{"pid":"fc12f98c94fb195fae210bc6304f8a71493357b8","tid":2173843,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f405afa15fac4b304441ea1513ae97e1df6d00","tid":2173843,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"取消左立法會選舉即刻冇哂啲確診"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"所以一定係政治肺炎"},{"pid":"ce638e9dfaba66ef2f3c8aea82e9255881bba173","tid":2173843,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0f405afa15fac4b304441ea1513ae97e1df6d00","tid":2173843,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:05:20.000Z","msg":"取消左立法會選舉即刻冇哂啲確診"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:07:22.000Z","msg":"真係無返咁上下IQ都估唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8974bbc0a23fdb305c8e5d56961b9af78be55c37","tid":2173843,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:15:49.000Z","msg":"病毒有潛服期，每7-14日一個cycle差唔多"},{"pid":"2b6f350365f0fe53500a857710b4ac7e3af82